---
---

<section id="about" class="relative py-24 md:py-32 bg-black overflow-hidden border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-accent-700/10 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="container mx-auto relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 mb-6 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] text-xs font-medium text-white/70">
          About Nelexa
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-heading text-white tracking-tighter mb-6">
          One partner. <span class="gradient-text italic">Every layer.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Nelexa is an enterprise infrastructure company built on a simple idea: the people who source your hardware, the people who rack it, and the people who keep the network humming should all work for the same team.
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          That's how we operate — from procurement and assembly, to colocation and IP transit, to dedicated server deployments in Dallas and New York. No handoffs, no finger-pointing, no gaps. Just senior engineers who answer the phone and infrastructure that stays up.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="/case-studies" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 border border-white/10 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors">
            Read Case Studies
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-500 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors">
            Talk to Sales
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="glass-card p-6">
          <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-lg bg-primary-600/20 border border-primary-500/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-primary-300">
              <path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Mission-Critical</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">Engineered for workloads where downtime costs real money.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card p-6">
          <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-lg bg-primary-600/20 border border-primary-500/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-primary-300">
              <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
              <line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"></line>
              <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"></line>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Full Stack</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">Hardware, colocation, networking — one team, one invoice.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card p-6">
          <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-lg bg-primary-600/20 border border-primary-500/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-primary-300">
              <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"></path>
              <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">US Coverage</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">Dallas and New York facilities on a carrier-diverse backbone.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card p-6">
          <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-lg bg-primary-600/20 border border-primary-500/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-primary-300">
              <path d="M18 8h1a4 4 0 0 1 0 8h-1"></path>
              <path d="M2 8h16v9a4 4 0 0 1-4 4H6a4 4 0 0 1-4-4V8z"></path>
              <line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="4"></line>
              <line x1="10" y1="1" x2="10" y2="4"></line>
              <line x1="14" y1="1" x2="14" y2="4"></line>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Senior-Only</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">Real engineers on the phone — never a script, never a tier-1.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
